overview: Prince Siegfried, who is drawn to the banks of a mysterious lake by his evil and dark self, meets Odette, the most beautiful swan in the world, and swears a love affair with her. Meanwhile, in the castle, bridesmaids are trying to please the distracted prince, but among them, the alluring swan 'Odilet' threatens the oath of love 'Siegfried' made to 'Odette'...
title: Swan Lake
